TestNG--- unit test framework & its is open source

it is available in the form of JAR files

it is also known as java unit testing framework

it is also known as TDD ( Test driven development ) frame work

purpose 

-- design testcases in a systematic way
-- To generate HTML reports
-- It gives different annotations
-- We can define the priority ie which tetscases to be executed first
-- Also the sequence of the testcase we can define
-- We can define the dependency
-- We can define grouping
-- Data provider feature is alos there